CatDescriptText: Cutline for related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 4, 1958, pg. A7, reads: "Los Jovenes Amigos Ball - The Los Jovenes Amigos Club sponsored a Snowflake Ball at the East Liberty YMCA, Dec. 20. The fellows and girls, out of school only a few hours earlier for the holiday, began the Christmas festivities with a bang. The club president is Nelson Harrison, Westinghouse High School senior. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of woman and students, members of Los Jovenes Amigos Club, including Westinghouse High School senior Nelson Harrison squatting second from left, posed during Snowflake Ball at East Liberty YMCA
